# Documentation (keep important ones, ignore generated)
# Keep: README.md, DEPLOYMENT_*.md, VPS_RECOMMENDATION.md, SECURITY_*.md
# Ignore: Most .md files in root (too many documentation files)

# Keep specific important docs
!README.md
!DEPLOYMENT_*.md
!VPS_RECOMMENDATION.md
!SECURITY_*.md
!ARCHITECTURE.md
!API_DOCUMENTATION.md

# Package manager files
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
pnpm-lock.yaml

